Reference

All functions

DEM_request()

returns a data frame with metadata and links to the Digital Elevation Models in a given polygon

county_names

Counties in Poland

geocodePL_get()

returns a list with metadata and coordinates for a given type of input (geocoding addresses and objects)

geodb_download()

downloads General Geographic Databases for entire voivodeships

geonames_download()

downloads State Register of Geographical Names

models3D_download()

downloads 3D models of buildings for counties

orto_request()

returns a data frame with metadata and links to the orthoimages in a given polygon

parcel_get()

returns a simple feature geometry for a given TERYT (ID) or coordinates

pointDTM100_download()

downloads Digital Terrain Models with 100 m resolution for entire voivodeships

pointDTM_get()

returns a data frame with vector points and terrain elevation for a given polygon

tile_download()

downloads tiles based on the data frame obtained using the orto_request() and DEM_request() functions

topodb_download()

downloads Topographic Databases for counties

voivodeship_names

Voivodeships in Poland
